data.name: rtbInstruct.Text
data.value:
Reach your goal SnL Game is a multi-player game between colleagues completing against each other.
The actions of each player are translated into dice rolls. The winner is the person who, with a bit of luck, makes it to the end of the game. Ladders can give you a boost but beware of snakes!
The state of the game is saved between sessions.
Reach your goal SnL is based on forked code: https://github.com/ccqi/Snakes-and-Ladders.
Source Code for this version: https://github.com/chribonn/Reach-your-goal-SnL
